{"id":22375,"date":"2024-10-28T17:09:11","date_gmt":"2024-10-28T11:39:11","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/?p=22375"},"modified":"2025-07-04T14:40:17","modified_gmt":"2025-07-04T09:10:17","slug":"materials-master-data-management","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/materials-master-data-management\/","title":{"rendered":"Materials Master Data Management"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"22375\" class=\"elementor elementor-22375\" data-elementor-post-type=\"post\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a3fa027 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a3fa027\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-660f057 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"660f057\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Data holds the key that can dictate the success or failure of a company. Ensuring that its quality is maintained is of utmost importance for the smooth functioning of organizations and maximum value generation. With asset-intensive and manufacturing companies evolving daily, the challenges of maintaining good data quality are increasing both in number and complexity. These asset-intensive firms maintain material inventory data that can directly impact day-to-day manufacturing and factory operations. The growth in these businesses leads to an increase in the volume and complexity of inventory and material data, making it a bigger challenge to manage and maintain a high-quality material master.<\/p><p>In this article, we cover the genesis of material data management, how this approach helps drive organizational efficiency, the data-management strategies enterprises can deploy to build excellence across production, maintenance and raw material management.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-775df65 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"775df65\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Evolution of Materials Management<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-856dffc e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"856dffc\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac14b7c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ac14b7c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Master Data Management (MDM), as a discipline, emerged in the early 2000s as organizations began to recognize the need for consistent, accurate, and timely data across their operations.\u00a0<\/p><p>Initially, this discipline was primarily focused on customer and product master data, the concept gradually expanded to include materials and MRO Spares for maximizing production and plant level efficiency, leading to the development of <b>Materials Master Data Management (MMDM) <\/b>as a separate branch.\u00a0\u00a0<\/p><p>The evolution of MMDM came traced back to several factors:<\/p><p class=\"whitespace-pre-wrap break-words\">The emergence of Materials Master Data Management (MMDM) as a specialized discipline arose directly from severe operational challenges that organizations faced when dealing with materials information. These pain points not only created the need for MMDM but continue to drive its evolution today.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-df7887a e-con-full form1 e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"df7887a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-79d0751 e-con-full form1 e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"79d0751\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-71a17ba e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"71a17ba\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a60c3d5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a60c3d5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Book a Consultation with our Materials Master Professional<\/span>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f4b9044 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f4b9044\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Proof of Concept on your Own Sample Data<\/span>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c58eb12 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c58eb12\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9385c34 elementor-widget elementor-widget-metform\" data-id=\"9385c34\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"metform.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mf-response-props-id-23691\" data-previous-steps-style=\"\" data-editswitchopen=\"\" data-response_type=\"alert\" data-erroricon