2v14h-2z\"><\/path><path d=\"m33 5h2v14h-2z\"><\/path><\/g><\/svg>\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span  >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSupplier Information\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-icon-box-description\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tPreferred vendors, lead times, and pricing.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a5f9e14 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a5f9e14\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e2158a3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e2158a3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div><p>The concept of materials master data is closely associated with <a href=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/erp-master-data-management\/\">enterprise resource planning (ERP) systems data management,<\/a> and one of the first companies to develop such systems was SAP.\u00a0<\/p><p>SAP introduced the idea of a centralized database for managing various business processes, including materials management. Their software allowed companies to maintain comprehensive materials master data, streamlining operations and improving efficiency across supply chain and production activities. Other ERP providers, like Oracle and Microsoft, also adopted similar concepts later on.<\/p><p>To put it simply, organizations encounter various challenges that MMDM addresses. We&#8217;ve detailed some of them below.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c3507b6 elementor-vertical-align-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\" data-id=\"c3507b6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span  >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tData Silos\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-icon-box-description\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tDifferent departments often maintain separate datasets, leading to inconsistencies. MMDM integrates data across functions, ensuring a single source of truth.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-55bc511 elementor-vertical-align-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\" data-id=\"55bc511\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span  >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tInaccurate Data\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-icon-box-description\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tPoor data quality can result in misinformed decisions, costly errors, and operational inefficiencies. MMDM implements data governance practices to enhance data accuracy and reliability.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ebed963 elementor-vertical-align-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\" data-id=\"ebed963\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span  >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tInefficient Processes\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-icon-box-description\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tManual data entry and management processes can be time-consuming and error-prone. MMDM automates workflows, improving efficiency and reducing the burden on employees.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-98179aa elementor-vertical-align-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\" data-id=\"98179aa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span  >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tLimited Visibility\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-icon-box-description\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tOrganizations often struggle with real-time visibility into material availability, leading to production delays. MMDM provides real-time insights, enabling better inventory management and procurement strategies.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-496eca8 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"496eca8\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ae69cb9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ae69cb9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"2945\" data-end=\"3656\">Unfortunately, many organizations don\u2019t fully appreciate the vital role materials play in keeping supply chains running smoothly. Often considered a non-core factor, companies neglect investing in material data management until issues arise. This outlook is now changing, with companies finally realizing the business value and savings that centralized, automated, well-maintained master data can generate. Thanks to technological advances like automation and machine learning in the MMDM (Material Master Data Management) space, master data management solution providers like Verdantis are transforming and upgrading material masters through data cleansing initiatives and corporate data governance strategies.<\/p><p data-start=\"3658\" data-end=\"4037\">Verdantis empowers businesses to unlock the full potential of their operations through streamlined processes, enhanced decision-making, and optimized resource utilization. As a dedicated service provider, Verdantis not only addresses the challenges posed by evolving data landscapes but also propels organizations toward a future where data becomes a strategic asset for success.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-60137c6 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"60137c6\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6e7f24a elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"6e7f24a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Materials-Master-Data-Management-2-1024x1024.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-27818\" alt=\"Materials Master Data Management\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Materials-Master-Data-Management-2-1024x1024.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Materials-Master-Data-Management-2-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Materials-Master-Data-Management-2-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Materials-Master-Data-Management-2-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Materials-Master-Data-Management-2-24x24.png 24w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Materials-Master-Data-Management-2-48x48.png 48w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Materials-Master-Data-Management-2-96x96.png 96w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/Materials-Master-Data-Management-2.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bd297c2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bd297c2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Many organisations still rely on multiple backend systems to support their supply chain. They have evolved over decades by incorporating the best of breed ERP systems, procurement software, and application management systems, resulting in multiple platforms with large amounts of data splashed across the organisation. Although the same data is being used across different systems, the simple fact that it is spread so heavily, raises questions as to which data is the &#8220;right&#8221; data. Data management becomes difficult due to inconsistency and poor visibility leading to an incomplete inventory, causing needless purchases and disruption in manufacturing processes, invariably increasing transaction costs.\u00a0 Ineffective business decisions taken due to disparate data can also lead to loss of competitive advantage.<\/p><p>The best way to overcome these issues is utilising material master data management. Material master ensures data standardisation and is a centralised repository which reduces data redundancy and can be used by various other applications in the enterprise such as purchasing, inventory management, invoicing etc. The main advantage of having a centralised source is that the data is clean and reliable and helps to maintain an accurate material inventory. It provides a single view of the material data to the entire organisation which will ensure the supply chain operations are more efficient leading to higher revenue and lower cost.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-15813af elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"15813af\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"279\" src=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/ERP-Implementation-1024x357.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-33709\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/ERP-Implementation-1024x357.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/ERP-Implementation-300x105.png 300w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/ERP-Implementation-768x268.png 768w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/ERP-Implementation-1536x536.png 1536w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/ERP-Implementation-2048x714.png 2048w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/ERP-Implementation-18x6.png 18w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-65fa306 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"65fa306\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Although this is an ideal solution for better material master data management, there are challenges in enterprises which have both legacy systems and new software. If it&#8217;s a large organisation spread across multiple units in multiple locations, before deciding on an MDM tool, the first thing to be done is to have a proper definition of what master data is and also adopt some standards to ensure data quality.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6a8cea8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6a8cea8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Data Management during ERP Implementation\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-78b8c44 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"78b8c44\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"178\" data-end=\"651\">the integration of Material Master Data Management into ERP implementation is not just a value add &#8211; it\u2019s a necessity. As organizations embark on enterprise-level initiatives such as ERP implementation or consolidation, clean and reliable data becomes the cornerstone of success. Yet, despite its critical importance, MDM is often left out of ERP blueprints, leading to missed opportunities, prolonged timelines, and increased costs.<\/p><p data-start=\"653\" data-end=\"1139\">One of the most significant opportunities in aligning MDM with ERP is cost control. Businesses are constantly seeking ways to reduce operational costs and enhance profitability. By cleansing, standardizing, and enriching data before it enters the ERP system, companies eliminate redundancy, avoid costly errors, and streamline procurement and inventory processes. This cost efficiency translates directly into a competitive edge, especially in markets where margin pressure is high.<\/p><p data-start=\"1141\" data-end=\"1511\">Another key benefit is process integration. In many organizations, departments operate in silos with disconnected systems and inconsistent data standards. Integrating MDM breaks down these barriers, enabling seamless communication across business units and geographies. The result is improved collaboration, more efficient workflows, and greater operational agility.<\/p><p data-start=\"1513\" data-end=\"2020\">Data is also the lifeblood of modern enterprises, and managing it effectively is fundamental to strategy execution. Companies that invest in MDM are better equipped to manage their objectives, identify opportunities, and adapt to change. This is especially crucial during ERP implementations, where data must be migrated from multiple systems, locations, and languages. Without proper cleansing and harmonization, data inconsistencies can delay implementation, lower ROI, and even cause system failures.<\/p><p data-start=\"2022\" data-end=\"2546\">MDM addresses these risks by ensuring data integration and governance from day one. ERP systems, by themselves, do not provide adequate tools to manage complex data structures. MDM solutions tailored to specific domains fill this gap by offering capabilities such as automated classification, normalization, and validation. Furthermore, integrating data governance into the ERP process ensures that only reliable, accurate, and consistent data enters the system &#8211; reducing risk and setting the stage for long-term success.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1a22565 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1a22565\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>MDM in the ERP Implementation Lifecycle<\/strong><\/p><p>Integrating Master Data Management with an ERP system can deliver many significant benefits to an enterprise. The below mentioned statistics are part of research done by Aberdeen which reveal the improvements that are possible during a Master Data Management initiative with ERP implementation.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9361d16 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"9361d16\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"277\" src=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/MDM-ERP-Integrated-1024x354.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-33700\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/MDM-ERP-Integrated-1024x354.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/MDM-ERP-Integrated-300x104.png 300w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/MDM-ERP-Integrated-768x265.png 768w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/MDM-ERP-Integrated-1536x530.png 1536w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/MDM-ERP-Integrated-2048x707.png 2048w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/MDM-ERP-Integrated-18x6.png 18w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-795bcec elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"795bcec\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Optimized ROI from ERP implementation with MDM Integrated<\/b><\/p><p>Based on earlier detailed statistics, it can be easily concluded that implementing an MDM initiative during an ERP implementation using automated solutions that combine AI-based technology and deep domain expertise can ensure the success of the project. Master Data Management can unlock the true potential of an ERP implementation project and achieve expected results.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3552115 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"3552115\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c66a2a0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"c66a2a0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"291\" src=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/MDM-ERP-1024x373.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-33701\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/MDM-ERP-1024x373.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/MDM-ERP-300x109.png 300w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/MDM-ERP-768x280.png 768w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/MDM-ERP-1536x560.png 1536w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/MDM-ERP-2048x746.png 2048w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/MDM-ERP-18x7.png 18w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-00c8420 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"00c8420\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Who Owns The Material Master Within An Asset-intensive Organization?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9766a0f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9766a0f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The answer to this question quite frankly adds another layer of complexity in effectively managing this specific domain.<\/p><p>Material master data is proprietary to divisions such as:<\/p><ul><li>IT (Supply Chain)<\/li><li>Plant Supervisors\/ Inventory Managers<\/li><li>Procurement<\/li><li>Centre of Excellence (Operations)<\/li><\/ul><p>Having multiple divisions administering material master data causes a lot of confusion within an organization.<\/p><p>To be competitive and overcome such challenge organizations need to adapt to a contoured path that is achievable by investing time and money in material master data cleansing.<\/p><p>Engaging with Service providers for data cleaning specific to the material domain is a step taken in the right direction.<\/p><p>The magnitude of clean, robust granular material master data seamlessly improves operational efficiencies increases the chances of optimizing inventory management.<\/p><p>The ideology is clear investing in material master data will significantly impact an organization&#8217;s visibility into its hand quality inventory with a premium ROI.<\/p><p>The trick to achieving positive results through this initiative is by choosing the right technology that helps you automate the management process of your Item master.<\/p><p>Automation from a technology perspective means:<\/p><p>1)\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Automating the process for a consistent data quality output<\/p><p>2)\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 The technology should be evolving, and be deployable for maximum return on investment.<\/p><p>3)\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Ensure systems can scale with an operation.<\/p><p>With the forested growth and increasing importance in master data just around the corner businesses should look to explore domain specific associates who can help them leverage sizeable ROI.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3339253 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3339253\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why Organizations Are Investing in MMDM<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3714be3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3714be3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"144\" data-end=\"549\">Organizations across asset-intensive industries are realizing that clean, consistent, and centralized material data is no longer a nice-to-have &#8211; it\u2019s a necessity. With growing inventories, complex supply chains, and mounting pressure to optimize operations, companies are turning to Materials Master Data Management (MMDM) to gain control over their material records and drive enterprise-wide efficiencies.<\/p><p data-start=\"551\" data-end=\"986\">The following examples showcase how leading companies are actively investing in MMDM initiatives- not just as a one-time clean-up effort, but as a long-term strategic capability. These real-world scenarios demonstrate the practical reasons behind their investments: from reducing excess inventory and preventing duplicate purchases, to enabling predictive maintenance, improving sourcing decisions, and ensuring seamless ERP upgrades.<\/p><p data-start=\"988\" data-end=\"1112\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Each case underlines a common realization &#8211; poor material data is a hidden cost, and fixing it unlocks immense business value.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1e0c3ce e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1e0c3ce\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-76e6023 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"76e6023\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-47030d5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"47030d5\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6b5c011 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6b5c011\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Download the Free Whitepaper<\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e0fab5b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e0fab5b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"> Next-Gen Material Master Data Management<\/span>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-934bc4b elemento