t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e0af1eb elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e0af1eb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">THE BUSINESS CASE FOR MATERIAL MASTER DATA MANAGEMENT<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7cb6352 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7cb6352\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Research from leading analyst firms have found that reduced material costs and optimized inventory, enabled by harmonized and subsequently maintained material master data, can contribute more than 1\/3<sup>rd<\/sup> of the hard dollar savings from an ERP consolidation initiative.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-777a361 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"777a361\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"432\" src=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/ERP.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-33732\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/ERP.jpg 887w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/ERP-300x162.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/ERP-768x415.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/ERP-18x10.jpg 18w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e52ed81 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e52ed81\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Success Metrics for Business Led Material Master Data Quality with MDG<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cdc4db6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"cdc4db6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Let\u2019s get to some real numbers based on more than 50 implementations.<\/p><p><strong><u>Increasing spend under management (Reducing Maverick Spend)<\/u><\/strong><\/p><p>It\u2019s not uncommon to see 30-50% maverick spend in the various industries we serve.\u00a0 A common goal is to reduce the maverick spend by 50% each year for three years.\u00a0 Business value \u2013 Maverick Spend is typically 17% higher than managed spending.<\/p><p>To pull these kinds of numbers off \u2013 you need both the DATA QUALITY Levels to increase the accuracy of the overall material master, and the MDG search capabilities to embrace heritage organization nomenclature with current taxonomies and attributes.<\/p><p><strong><u>Reducing MRO Inventory<\/u><\/strong><\/p><p>Identification of exact duplicates can realize 4% to 8% of MRO inventory levels.<\/p><p>Identification of near-exact, or \u201cform, fit and function\u201d duplicates can realize an additional 6% to 12% of MRO.<\/p><p>To keep inventories from getting bloated in the future, the MDG solution needs to be able to identify these \u201cform, fit and function\u201d in real-time.<\/p><p><strong><u>Leveraging Economies of Scale<\/u><\/strong><\/p><p>Global Purchasing departments need to be able to look at demand from a level beyond supplier names, and sometimes even beyond manufacturer names \u2013 they need to be able to line up technical attributes to identify best quality at best cost and increase volumes through those channels.\u00a0 A material master specific DATA QUALITY effort drives this granular visibility and a material master specific MDG drives reporting and analysis to make this easy on the commodity managers (let\u2019s face it \u2013 getting down to technical characteristics exponentially increases data points for analysis \u2013 the tool should do that heavy lifting for you \u2013 right?).<\/p><p>Economies of scale \u2013 through VLAs, or even hedged buying drives 5% to 15% gains in savings and the MDG framework can help guide new requests to preferred contracted suppliers.<\/p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Reducing New Requests and Approval Turn-Around<\/strong><\/span><\/p><p>This is all about improved performance and hard dollar savings associated with<\/p><ol><li>Finding the right items in inventory<\/li><li>Expediting new item additions<\/li><\/ol><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>The DATA QUALITY effort cleans up the material master (\u201cGet it Clean\u201d) which drives search-ability to new levels. Further, implanting the MDG framework to block duplicates and find \u201cform, fit and function\u201d alternatives is key here.\u00a0 Reduction in extraneous new item requests by 75% is realistic within 12 months.<\/p><p>Speeding up the process from initial request for a new material, through the approval process, and its entry in the ERP\/EAM system is somewhat dependent on the number of approvals needed, but using an MDG framework that leverages dashboards, a robust workflow and flexible notifications is far superior to routing forms in emails.\u00a0 Robust workflow management expedites, routes, and pools requests.\u00a0 We have seen customers reduce the time for addition from 7 business days to 4 hours.\u00a0<\/p><p>The hard currency savings are tied to reduced expedited shipping and reduced p-card usage at local suppliers, not to mention any actual outages or delayed maintenance related costs.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-251d23c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"251d23c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d7a14b0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d7a14b0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Use Case: A Global Oil &amp; Gas Giant<\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2008625 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2008625\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"262\" data-end=\"605\">The oil and gas industry is highly consolidated, with a handful of major players controlling the majority of the market. Operations in this sector are capital- and resource-intensive, involving large-scale equipment and highly complex processes. Any disruption &#8211; however small- can have cascading effects on production, profitability, and safety.<\/p><p data-start=\"607\" data-end=\"1067\">One of the lesser-known but high-impact areas of risk lies in the quality and structure of material master data. This data doesn\u2019t just include product identifiers; it often encompasses specifications, manufacturer details, and pricing &#8211; information that directly supports procurement, planning, and maintenance functions. When inconsistencies or errors exist in this data, they can lead to incorrect purchases, production downtime, and millions in lost revenue.<\/p><h5 data-start=\"1069\" data-end=\"1091\"><strong data-start=\"1074\" data-end=\"1091\">The Challenge<\/strong><\/h5><p data-start=\"1093\" data-end=\"1498\">Company A, a global leader in petroleum extraction and refining with annual revenues exceeding $10 billion, operates a major refinery plant in Houston. This single facility contributes over $500 million annually in oil and petroleum products. To maintain uptime, a dedicated team manages procurement master data, including vendor information, spare parts, manufacturer details, and product specifications.<\/p><p data-start=\"1500\" data-end=\"1679\">Following a routine inspection, a maintenance engineer raised a request for an urgent replacement of a specific part:<br data-start=\"1617\" data-end=\"1620\" \/><strong data-start=\"1620\" data-end=\"1677\">\u201cBEARING, BALL; 20 MM ID; 47 MM OD; 26 MM WD; Radial\u201d<\/strong><\/p><p data-start=\"1681\" data-end=\"1842\">A procurement team member searched the ERP system and identified an existing item that seemed to match:<br data-start=\"1784\" data-end=\"1787\" \/><strong data-start=\"1787\" data-end=\"1842\">\u201cBRG, BALL; 20 MM ID; 47 MM OD; 26 MM WD; Standard\u201d<\/strong><\/p><p data-start=\"1844\" data-end=\"2144\">Assuming it was the same part, the team moved ahead with the procurement request. However, the critical difference<strong data-start=\"1959\" data-end=\"1986\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211;\u00a0<\/span>\u201cRadial\u201d vs. \u201cStandard\u201d<\/strong>-was overlooked. This small but vital detail could have resulted in the delivery of the wrong part, potential equipment failure, and unplanned plant downtime.<\/p><h5 data-start=\"2146\" data-end=\"2172\"><strong data-start=\"2151\" data-end=\"2172\">The MMDM Solution<\/strong><\/h5><p data-start=\"2174\" data-end=\"2522\">To mitigate such risks, the company partnered with a master data management expert to implement a materials-focused MDM strategy. One of the key changes was the categorization and normalization of all spare parts, particularly bearings. The team introduced mandatory attribute fields- such as \u201cbearing type\u201d- within the material governance framework.<\/p><p data-start=\"2524\" data-end=\"2718\">This simple data governance rule ensured that every new or modified part record included standardized technical attributes, reducing ambiguity and enforcing data quality from the point of entry.<\/p><h5 data-start=\"2720\" data-end=\"2744\"><strong data-start=\"2725\" data-end=\"2744\">Business Impact<\/strong><\/h5><ul data-start=\"2746\" data-end=\"3146\"><li data-start=\"2746\" data-end=\"2854\"><p data-start=\"2748\" data-end=\"2854\"><strong data-start=\"2748\" data-end=\"2793\">Dramatic reduction in stock discrepancies<\/strong> through consistent, attribute-based product identification<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2855\" data-end=\"2953\"><p data-start=\"2857\" data-end=\"2953\"><strong data-start=\"2857\" data-end=\"2906\">Improved forecasting and maintenance planning<\/strong> with trustworthy historical consumption data<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2954\" data-end=\"3044\"><p data-start=\"2956\" data-end=\"3044\"><strong data-start=\"2956\" data-end=\"2989\">Optimized safety stock levels<\/strong> based on accurate lead times and part usage patterns<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3045\" data-end=\"3146\"><p data-start=\"3047\" data-end=\"3146\"><strong data-start=\"3047\" data-end=\"3076\">Lowered obsolescence risk<\/strong> through better visibility into the product lifecycle and alternates<\/p><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fb02bf3 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"fb02bf3\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-16a8b4b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"16a8b4b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Use Case: Food &amp; Beverage Conglomerate Prevents Downtime with Smarter Material Master Data Management<\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a29ad69 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a29ad69\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"253\" data-end=\"576\">In the food and beverage industry, where safety, speed, and precision are paramount, even the smallest oversight can have far-reaching consequences. With tight production schedules, strict quality controls, and regulatory compliance requirements, maintaining clean, complete, and accurate material master data is essential.<\/p><h4 data-start=\"578\" data-end=\"600\"><strong data-start=\"583\" data-end=\"600\">The Challenge<\/strong><\/h4><p data-start=\"602\" data-end=\"992\">Company B, a major food and beverage conglomerate, operates a high-capacity manufacturing plant in the Midwest. This facility produces a wide range of packaged goods &#8211; beverages, sauces, frozen meals &#8211; and plays a key role in the company\u2019s global supply chain. With annual revenues exceeding $5 billion, the plant runs multiple production lines around the clock to meet growing consumer demand.<\/p><p data-start=\"994\" data-end=\"1262\">During a routine inspection of a bottling line, a maintenance technician flagged a worn-out pump as needing immediate replacement. This particular pump played a critical role in the beverage filling and sealing process &#8211; any failure could lead to a full production halt.<\/p><p data-start=\"1264\" data-end=\"1410\">The technician entered the part specifications into the ERP system and selected a pump labeled:<br data-start=\"1359\" data-end=\"1362\" \/><strong data-start=\"1362\" data-end=\"1410\">\u201cPump, Centrifugal; 30 GPM; Stainless Steel\u201d<\/strong><\/p><p data-start=\"1412\" data-end=\"1603\">However, the part that arrived was not rated for food-grade applications &#8211; a crucial oversight. The correct item should have been:<br data-start=\"1540\" data-end=\"1543\" \/><strong data-start=\"1543\" data-end=\"1603\">\u201cPump, Centrifugal; 30 GPM; Stainless Steel; Food-Grade\u201d<\/strong><\/p><p data-start=\"1605\" data-end=\"1939\">Because the system lacked proper attribute differentiation and enforcement in the material master, the technician and procurement team assumed the existing item was suitable. If installed, the incorrect pump could have contaminated the product or failed regulatory checks &#8211; triggering costly recalls, shutdowns, and reputational damage.<\/p><h4 data-start=\"1941\" data-end=\"1972\"><strong data-start=\"1946\" data-end=\"1972\">Potential Consequences<\/strong><\/h4><ul data-start=\"1974\" data-end=\"2264\"><li data-start=\"1974\" data-end=\"2043\"><p data-start=\"1976\" data-end=\"2043\">Installation of a non-food-grade pump in a food-grade environment<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2044\" data-end=\"2107\"><p data-start=\"2046\" data-end=\"2107\">Risk of product contamination and regulatory non-compliance<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2108\" data-end=\"2160\"><p data-start=\"2110\" data-end=\"2160\">Emergency production shutdown and cleaning cycle<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2161\" data-end=\"2209\"><p data-start=\"2163\" data-end=\"2209\">Missed shipping deadlines and reduced output<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2210\" data-end=\"2264\"><p data-start=\"2212\" data-end=\"2264\">Millions in lost revenue and possible legal exposure<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h4 data-start=\"2266\" data-end=\"2292\"><strong data-start=\"2271\" data-end=\"2292\">The MMDM Solution<\/strong><\/h4><p data-start=\"2294\" data-end=\"2471\">Recognizing the gap, the company worked with a materials master data management expert to implement a structured, attribute-driven approach to cataloging its material inventory.<\/p><p data-start=\"2473\" data-end=\"2638\">The new governance model introduced mandatory data fields and attribute-level validation within the MMDM framework. For pumps, this included clear classification by:<\/p><ul data-start=\"2640\" data-end=\"2845\"><li data-start=\"2640\" data-end=\"2688\"><p data-start=\"2642\" data-end=\"2688\"><strong data-start=\"2642\" data-end=\"2655\">Pump Type<\/strong> (e.g., Centrifugal, Diaphragm)<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2689\" data-end=\"2725\"><p data-start=\"2691\" data-end=\"2725\"><strong data-start=\"2691\" data-end=\"2708\">Flow Capacity<\/strong> (e.g., 30 GPM)<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2726\" data-end=\"2778\"><p data-start=\"2728\" data-end=\"2778\"><strong data-start=\"2728\" data-end=\"2752\">Material Composition<\/strong> (e.g., Stainless Steel)<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2779\" data-end=\"2845\"><p data-start=\"2781\" data-end=\"2845\"><strong data-start=\"2781\" data-end=\"2805\">Certification Status<\/strong> (e.g., Food-Grade, Standard Industrial)<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"2847\" data-end=\"3097\">With these standardized attributes in place, any procurement request involving a pump now automatically checks for compatibility based on application requirements. For food production lines, only certified food-grade parts appear as eligible options.<\/p><h4 data-start=\"3099\" data-end=\"3123\"><strong data-start=\"3104\" data-end=\"3123\">Business Impact<\/strong><\/h4><ul data-start=\"3125\" data-end=\"3586\"><li data-start=\"3125\" data-end=\"3219\"><p data-start=\"3127\" data-end=\"3219\"><strong data-start=\"3127\" data-end=\"3161\">Elimination of ordering errors<\/strong> through standardized part classification and validation<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3220\" data-end=\"3322\"><p data-start=\"3222\" data-end=\"3322\"><strong data-start=\"3222\" data-end=\"3269\">Increased uptime and production reliability<\/strong> with the right part delivered on the first attempt<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3323\" data-end=\"3411\"><p data-start=\"3325\" data-end=\"3411\"><strong data-start=\"3325\" data-end=\"3360\">Improved procurement efficiency<\/strong> by reducing rework and urgent last-minute orders<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3412\" data-end=\"3504\"><p data-start=\"3414\" data-end=\"3504\"><strong data-start=\"3414\" data-end=\"3455\">Better compliance and audit readiness<\/strong> with clear visibility into part certifications<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3505\" data-end=\"3586\"><p data-start=\"3507\" data-end=\"3586\"><strong data-start=\"3507\" data-end=\"3525\">Enhanced trust<\/strong> across maintenance, procurement, and quality assurance teams<\/p><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0d3a3ff e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0d3a3ff\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9144df2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9144df2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Executing a Materials Master Data Management Strategy<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c630a51 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c630a51\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a2f7d93 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a2f7d93\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The roadmap to executing a fool-proof materials master data plan is not too different from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/master-data-management-strategies\/\">the strategies for managing master data<\/a> for suppliers, customers and products. However, industry-specific expertise, the turnaround time, testing the quality of the final output are all aspects that come into play specifically in Materials Master.<\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: var(--body-font);\">In theory, it&#8217;s simple &#8211; clean the &#8220;unreliable&#8221; data in the system; test the cleaned data thoroughly based on the predefined rules for uniqueness, categorization and completeness. Once the same has been mapped in the ERP, ensure that &#8220;Robust Data Governance Systems&#8221; are put in place to ensure the data doesn&#8217;t &#8220;contaminate&#8221; in a similar manner overtime.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: var(--body-font);\">This can be done in-house with professionals who understand the MRO requirements along with database and IT professionals. However, not all companies have access to this kind of talent, and sometimes even when they do, they prefer working with a specialist with a deep understanding of materials master and the various <a href=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/master-data-governance\/\">data governance principles<\/a> that go along with it, like Verdantis. We&#8217;ll cover a bit more about Verdantis&#8217; MMDM solutions a bit later in this article.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6689dca e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"6689dca\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e01804 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2e01804\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Materials Data Cleansing<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d013693 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"d013693\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-488201e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"488201e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Due to absence of Data Governance Strategies and Data Stewardship, over time, an organizations&#8217; &#8220;Materials Master Data&#8221; gets &#8220;compromised&#8221;.\u00a0\u00a0<\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: var(--body-font);\">This means, over time, repeated procurement requests for the same part would have resulted in &#8220;Duplicates&#8221; in the system. This may have happened due to poor categorization when the first procurement request was first placed in the ERP system. Missing details like the &#8220;Manufacturer Part Number&#8221; or &#8220;Manufacturer\/Supplier Name&#8221; compounds this issue even further.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p>The solution to this problem has so far relied on good ol&#8217; data cleansing &#8211; This has largely been manual and relied mainly on pattern matching, fuzzy matching various data points and running some &#8220;spreadsheet magic&#8221; on the data. <span data-teams=\"true\">Effective management of both material and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/customer-master-data-management\/\">customer master data<\/a> improves operating efficiency by removing duplications, decreasing errors and downtime, and leading to smoother, more efficient collaboration between sales, production, procurement, logistics, and customer service organizations.<\/span><\/p><p>However with the advancement in AI in the last couple of years, at Verdantis, we&#8217;ve been deploying industry-specific trained Machine Learning models for cleansing, standardizing, harmonizing and enriching materials master and this has improved not only the efficiency in delivering these projects but also the accuracy and reliability of the materials master.\u00a0<\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: var(--body-font);\">Verdantis&#8217; state-of-the-art <strong>Harmonize<\/strong><\/span><strong>\u00a9<\/strong> suite ingests material records in minutes and processes it within a few hours, based on the input rules provided. This data is then manually verified to ensure total accuracy before being updated in the ERP system.<\/p><p>The video below does a great job at explaining how Verdanits&#8217; Harmonize Suite can cleanse your legacy master data records that are now unreliable.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-813ca7d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"813ca7d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;shape_divider_top&quot;:&quot;split&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-shape elementor-shape-top\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-negative=\"false\">\n\t\t\t<svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 20\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\">\n\t<path class=\"elementor-shape-fill\" d=\"M0,0v3c0,0,393.8,0,483.4,0c9.2,0,16.6,7.4,16.6,16.6c0-9.1,7.4-16.6,16.6-16.6C606.2,3,1000,3,1000,3V0H0z\"\/>\n<\/svg>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-596b925 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"596b925\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Benefits of implementing the Data Cleansing Initiative\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6f87e92 e-grid e-con-full e-con e-child\" data-id=\"6f87e92\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-711b23b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"711b23b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Annual Inventory Carry cost reductions of 4.4% <\/b>(Factored cost of capital) as write-down (Positive impact to balance sheet)<\/p><ul><li>400 Million in Inventory<\/li><li>10% Duplicate Identification<\/li><li>40 Million in Duplicate Inventory value<\/li><li>Write Down of Factored Costs at 4.4% of 40 Million = <b>$1,760,000<\/b><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0d6b3a3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-video\" data-id=\"0d6b3a3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;youtube_url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/www.youtube.com\\\/watch?v=rJmy3Gjbltg&quot;,&quot;video_type&quot;:&quot;youtube&quot;,&quot;controls&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"video.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-wrapper elementor-open-inline\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-video\"><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-16f6ef9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"16f6ef9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Cost Reduction on aggregation of demand <\/b>across 15% of $1BN in MRO<\/p><ul><li>1 Billion in Maintenance, Repair and Operations Material<\/li><li>15% Identified through Harmonization as Similar (Across 10% Supplier Base)<\/li><li>150 Million addressable spend<\/li><li>12.5% reduction in costs through strategic sourcing<\/li><li>Cost Reduction of 12.5% of $150 Million = <b>$18,000,000<\/b><\/li><\/ul><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>ANNUALIZED NET COST REDUCTIONS FROM : <b>DATA CLEANSING = $19,760,000<\/b><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-088d5f6 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"088d5f6\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b61a0c1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b61a0c1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Materials Data Governance<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1e9f8ab e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"1e9f8ab\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-030689d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"030689d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>While Harmonize ensures that historical materials data is cleaned and kept up-to-date, a robust data governance strategy is what will ensure that such errors are prevented and every material request in the future is &#8220;complete&#8221; with the relevant data points without duplicating the material records.\u00a0<\/p><p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">Typically, the &#8220;Data Steward&#8221; or the &#8220;Head of Master Data&#8221; is responsible for this governance.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: var(--body-font);\">Generally speaking, enterprises tend to have systems in place within their ERP to ensure these &#8220;Governance Standards&#8221; are maintained. For enterprises using SAP, the governance system &#8220;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.sap.com\/india\/products\/technology-platform\/master-data-governance.html\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">SAP MDG<\/a>&#8221; can be leveraged for adhering to data governance standards. Similarly, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.oracle.com\/a\/ocom\/docs\/middleware\/data-integration\/oracle-data-governance-wp.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Oracle MDM<\/a> is also used for data governance at companies using Oracle for their ERP and MDM requirements.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: var(--body-font);\">The challenge is that these legacy systems typically require a team to maintain and setup. Additionally, building industry-specific requirements in these systems also become a bit complex and companies can face challenges while implementing them.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: var(--body-font);\">At Verdantis, our Governance software service, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/integrity\/\">Integrity<\/a><\/span>\u00a9, is a purpose-built data governance product for Materials Master Management that adapts to the the continuously evolving need of every Industry. The software product can be used as a <strong>bolt-on solution within <a href=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/sap-mdm\/\">SAP MDG<\/a><\/strong> and can be <strong>easily integrated directly into most ERPs<\/strong> as well. We&#8217;ve covered more on how they can be used together this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/master-data-management-with-verdantis-integrity-and-sap-mdg\/\">in this article<\/a>.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a645ff4 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a645ff4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_b